23:59.645 --> 24:02.523
This guy will lie to his last breath!

24:02.564 --> 24:05.859
Why shift blame to Schiller?
It's for what he's feeling!

24:05.901 --> 24:08.194
Y'know, I'm getting a headache.

24:08.236 --> 24:11.948
We have a convicted paedophile
saying he didn't molest anybody,

24:11.990 --> 24:14.659
