who might have.

24:14.700 --> 24:16.535
Maybe Dayton told the truth.

24:16.577 --> 24:19.538
Why? Cos paedophiles
are always so honest?

24:21.957 --> 24:24.960
Ask the girl. Where is she now?

24:36.762 --> 24:38.639
Over there.

24:45.020 --> 24:46.438
Hi.

24:49.899 --> 24:52.610
Whenever Mr Dayton stayed with my mom,

24:52.652 --> 24:57.615
