30:31.546 --> 30:33.548
Little Jimmy's a junior!

30:33.589 --> 30:38.052
Hm. You'll probably run into him.
They do a lot of studying together.

30:38.093 --> 30:40.220
Oh, no, no, no.

30:40.262 --> 30:42.556
El! Relax.

30:48.770 --> 30:51.272
Has Maureen had sex yet, do you know?

30:51.314 --> 30:53.357
God, I hope not.

30:55.651 --> 30:58.571
