35:57.595 --> 35:59.680
- Good night, Dad.
- Good night.

36:00.347 --> 36:02.808
- Don't wait up for me.
- Yeah, right.

36:18.197 --> 36:21.158
- Virginia?
- I'm upstairs.

36:32.126 --> 36:34.003
You wanted to talk to us?

36:37.339 --> 36:40.551
Thomas Dayton never touched you,
