36:40.592 --> 36:44.137
Tom. No. He didn't.

36:44.179 --> 36:46.473
It was Schiller? He raped you?

36:50.560 --> 36:55.564
Tell us. It changes everything
if Schiller sexually assaulted you.

36:59.610 --> 37:02.029
I wouldn't call it assault.

37:03.071 --> 37:06.700
We need to hear it in your words, Virginia.

37:06.741 --> 37:09.285
How did it start?

37:09.327 --> 37:13.331
Schiller would tell Mom and me
stories about his travels.

37:13.372 --> 37:16.584
We'd sit up late at night in the kitchen,

37:16.625 --> 37:22.172
listening about places
that had names like Kuala Lumpur

37:22.214 --> 37:24.508
and Burkina Faso.

37:24.549 --> 37:26.468
When did it get sexual, Virginia?

37:26.510 --> 37:28.553
July 17th.

37:29.345 --> 37:32.807
It was raining. Mom wasn't home.

37:32.849 --> 37:37.478
Schiller and I ordered Ethiopian food.
It was delicious.

37:37.520 --> 37:40.981
- And then what happened?
- I kissed him.

37:41.023 --> 37:44.234
- That's how it started.
- He coerced you?

37:44.276 --> 37:47.279
No. We couldn't help ourselves.

37:47.320 --> 37:51.532
I had never felt that... pull before.

37:54.160 --> 37:56.370
It's every man's fantasy, right?

37:56.412 --> 37:59.581
Having some young girl want him?

38:02.501 --> 38:07.088
But it was so much more than that.
For the first time in my life,

38:07.130 --> 38:10.425
making love... felt natural.

38:11.050 --> 38:12.927
Felt good.

38:13.553 --> 38:15.471
For the first time, I felt safe.

38:17.473 --> 38:20.809
- How long did it continue?
- Months.

38:20.851 --> 38:25.021
When he was home,
he made this house bearable.

38:25.856 --> 38:29.609
When he would leave,
I didn't think I'd make it without him.

38:31.694 --> 38:33.988
I cried every night he was gone.

38:34.030 --> 38:40.452
When he came back, he promised
he'd never leave me behind again.

38:41.286 --> 38:44.039
When he was out, I would read his mail.

38:44.081 --> 38:48.168
And saw that he was gonna leave again.
For Romania this time.

38:48.209 --> 38:50.670
- And?
- I packed my bag.

38:50.712 --> 38:53.381
I wanted him to take me with him.

38:53.423 --> 38:55.675
He was sitting right there.

38:59.678 --> 39:01.305
Tell me.

39:07.352 --> 39:09.813
Tell me what happened.

39:09.854 --> 39:11.731
I did

39:13.191 --> 39:15.067
what he liked.

39:16.110 --> 39:18.195
What's that?

39:19.863 --> 39:23.200
I got on his lap. The chair leans back.

39:25.494 --> 39:27.579
And when we were finished,

39:28.246 --> 39:32.166
I leaned close
and asked him to take me away.

39:32.208 --> 39:34.043
'You promised.'

39:35.920 --> 39:38.214
What did he say?

39:38.255 --> 39:40.549
He said he needed to travel light.

39:41.341 --> 39:45.137
And I knew I couldn't stay
another day here without him.

39:47.847 --> 39:51.100
Something broke inside me.

39:53.436 --> 39:57.898
I didn't think. I put my knee on his throat
and I held it there.

39:59.817 --> 40:04.988
He made this wet, hissing sound.
He couldn't talk.

40:10.535 --> 40:12.620
And when he was still,

40:13.496 --> 40:17.833
I picked up my underwear
from the floor and I put it in his mouth.

40:20.919 --> 40:23.463
And I left.

40:27.008 --> 40:29.010
He had this drive,

40:29.052 --> 40:32.221
this... impulse to travel.

40:33.681 --> 40:35.558
Like you.

40:37.643 --> 40:40.562
He'd always promised to take me away,

40:40.604 --> 40:43.273
to a place where he would love me.

40:44.316 --> 40:48.028
And I just wanted so badly to leave this life.

40:48.069 --> 40:50.363
Oh! I miss him!

41:02.207 --> 41:05.168
Yeah?

41:07.045 --> 41:09.547
- Tough day.
- Hm.

41:13.926 --> 41:17.430
They're arraigning Virginia in the morning.

41:17.471 --> 41:19.640
ADA's going for man two.

41:21.016 --> 41:23.101
You OK with that?

41:27.272 --> 41:28.982
Talk to me.

41:30.066 --> 41:33.528
