41:35.196 --> 41:38.741
When she was born,
I used to take her to the playground

41:38.782 --> 41:41.660
and the grocery store, whatever.

41:44.162 --> 41:47.707
But it wasn't her
that I would watch, obsessively.

41:48.958 --> 41:53.754
It was the men. All around.
To protect her from what they might do.

41:54.797 --> 41:57.299
- Elliot...
- The other night, erm,

41:58.342 --> 42:01.345
