42:01.386 --> 42:05.307
And all I'm thinking is,
what is this guy gonna do to her?

42:05.348 --> 42:07.309
I know.

42:07.350 --> 42:09.811
I made a mistake today.

42:12.313 --> 42:14.190
I didn't see it.

42:15.024 --> 42:17.443
