42:17.485 --> 42:19.820
You got too wrapped up.

42:21.280 --> 42:24.199
I saw that girl like I saw my daughter.

42:25.450 --> 42:27.535
As a victim.

42:27.577 --> 42:31.706
Not as someone capable of... acting,

42:33.374 --> 42:35.251
or feeling,

42:36.293 --> 42:38.504
loving on their own.

42:40.464 --> 42:45.052
Your daughter caring for someone
doesn't mean she loves you any less.

42:45.093 --> 42:49.722
